title: Roetter
description: Natural food store St. Hanshaugen park. Stocks a variety of vegetarian and vegan products. You will find tofu, tempeh, soyburgers, vegan hotdogs, non-dairy milk, soy yoghurt, vegan protein powder, rice, beans, seaweeds, non-dairy ice cream, fresh bread, juices, kombucha, yerba mate, and more.
